---
// One-question-per-session Italian HR interview across two interchangeable providers
// (HeyGen | Tavus). A candidate starts (or resumes with a code), answers one question per
// short timed session, and can pause between questions. Every utterance is persisted to
// local SQLite. The page is a small multi-screen state machine that never scrolls on Y.
import '../styles/brand.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>Interview Demo — HeyGen / Tavus</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="app" id="app" data-screen="start">
      <!-- ── START ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="screen panel" id="screen-start">
        <img src="/quint-logo.png" alt="Quint" class="brand-logo" />
        <h1 class="brand">Colloquio conoscitivo</h1>

        <div class="provider-toggle" role="radiogroup" aria-label="Provider">
          <label>
            <input type="radio" name="provider" value="heygen" checked />
            <span>HeyGen</span>
          </label>
          <label>
            <input type="radio" name="provider" value="tavus" />
            <span>Tavus</span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <label class="consent">
          <input type="checkbox" id="consent" />
          <span
            >Questa è una demo. Parlerai con un intervistatore AI; la conversazione viene
            trascritta e salvata localmente per analisi. Durante il colloquio la sessione è
            monitorata per integrità: la webcam resta attiva e vengono registrati segnali di
            presenza e attenzione (nessuna immagine lascia il tuo dispositivo). Procedendo,
            acconsenti.</span
          >
        </label>

        <div class="paths">
          <div class="path">
            <h2>Nuovo colloquio</h2>
            <input type="text" id="display-name" placeholder="Il tuo nome" autocomplete="name" />
            <button type="button" id="btn-new" class="btn primary">Inizia</button>
          </div>
          <div class="path-sep">oppure</div>
          <div class="path">
            <h2>Riprendi</h2>
            <input type="text" id="resume-code" placeholder="Codice (es. 7QK2PM)" maxlength="8" />
            <button type="button" id="btn-resume" class="btn">Riprendi</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p id="start-error" class="error-line"></p>
        <a href="/admin" class="admin-link">Archivio interviste →</a>
      </section>

      <!-- ── CODE (shown once after a new candidate is created) ────────────────── -->
      <section class="screen panel" id="screen-code">
        <h2>Salva questo codice</h2>
        <p class="hint">Ti servirà per riprendere il colloquio più tardi.</p>
        <p class="code-big" id="code-value">——————</p>
        <button type="button" id="btn-begin" class="btn primary">Inizia il colloquio</button>
      </section>

      <!-- ── RULES (pre-interview briefing — shown once before the first question) ── -->
      <section class="screen panel" id="screen-rules">
        <h2>Prima di iniziare</h2>
        <p class="hint">Questo colloquio è monitorato per garantire l'equità. Assicurati di:</p>
        <ul class="rules-list">
          <li>Essere solo/a nell'inquadratura della webcam</li>
          <li>Rimanere con il viso visibile e rivolto verso lo schermo</li>
          <li>Non cambiare scheda o finestra durante il colloquio</li>
          <li>Non copiare o incollare testo</li>
          <li>Rimanere in modalità schermo intero</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="rules-note">La webcam rimane attiva e vengono acquisiti snapshot periodici. Nessun video lascia il tuo dispositivo.</p>

        <!-- Start CTA: triggers the device check. Hidden once the test is running. -->
        <button type="button" id="btn-start-check" class="btn primary">Avvia il test</button>

        <!-- Device check panel: webcam preview + mic level meter. Hidden until the test starts. -->
        <div id="device-check" class="device-check" hidden>
          <div class="device-check-preview">
            <video id="device-preview" autoplay playsinline muted></video>
          </div>

          <div class="device-check-mic">
            <span class="device-check-mic-label">Parla per testare il microfono</span>
            <div class="mic-bar">
              <div id="mic-bar-fill" class="mic-bar-fill" data-ok="false"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="device-check-status">
            <li id="status-camera" class="status-item" data-ok="false">Webcam attiva</li>
            <li id="status-distance" class="status-item" data-ok="false">Distanza dalla webcam corretta</li>
            <li id="status-gaze" class="status-item" data-ok="false">Sguardo rivolto alla webcam</li>
            <li id="status-mic" class="status-item" data-ok="false">Microfono attivo</li>
          </ul>

          <p
            id="device-check-hint"
            class="device-check-hint"
            aria-live="polite"
            data-hint-far="Avvicinati alla webcam"
            data-hint-gaze="Guarda verso lo schermo"
          ></p>

          <p id="device-check-denied" class="device-check-denied" hidden>
            Permesso webcam o microfono bloccato. Riattivalo dalle impostazioni del sito
            del browser (clicca sull'icona del lucchetto nella barra degli indirizzi),
            poi ricarica la pagina. L'app non può richiederti di nuovo il permesso.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Entry CTA: gated on both camera and mic. Hidden until the check passes. -->
        <button type="button" id="btn-rules-ok" class="btn primary" hidden>Entra nel colloquio</button>
      </section>

      <!-- ── INTERVIEW ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class="screen interview" id="screen-interview">
        <header class="topbar">
          <span class="progress" id="progress">Domanda 1 di 7</span>
          <span class="completed" id="completed">✓ 0/7</span>
          <span class="timer" id="timer" data-warn="normal">—:——</span>
        </header>

        <section class="stage">
          <!-- Audio is attached to this same element, so it must NOT be muted. -->
          <video id="avatar-video" autoplay playsinline></video>

          <div id="meter" class="meter" hidden>
            <span class="meter-icon">⚡</span>
            <span id="meter-cost" class="meter-cost">$0.00</span>
            <span id="meter-credits" class="meter-credits" hidden></span>
          </div>

          <!-- Candidate self-view. The proctor collector owns this stream; the camera
               indicator is unsuppressable, so we show the feed to keep it expected.
               Hidden until the collector attaches a stream at session start. -->
          <video id="self-view" class="self-view" autoplay playsinline muted hidden></video>

          <p id="caption" class="caption"></p>
        </section>

        <footer class="bar">
          <p id="status" class="status" data-state="idle">pronta a iniziare</p>
          <button id="talk-button" class="pulsantone" type="button" data-on="false">
            🎤 Parla
          </button>
        </footer>
        <div id="toast" class="toast" hidden>
          <span id="toast-msg"></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── END OF QUESTION ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="screen panel" id="screen-endq">
        <h2 id="endq-title">Domanda conclusa</h2>
        <p class="hint" id="endq-hint">Vuoi continuare con la prossima domanda?</p>
        <div class="row">
          <button type="button" id="btn-next" class="btn primary">Prossima domanda</button>
          <button type="button" id="btn-pause" class="btn">Metti in pausa</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ── PAUSED ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="screen panel" id="screen-paused">
        <h2>Colloquio in pausa</h2>
        <p class="hint">Il tuo codice per riprendere più tardi:</p>
        <p class="code-big" id="paused-code">——————</p>
        <button type="button" id="btn-home" class="btn primary">Torna all'inizio</button>
      </section>

      <!-- ── DONE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="screen panel" id="screen-done">
        <h2>Colloquio completato 🎉</h2>
        <p class="hint">Grazie per il tuo tempo! Le risposte sono salvate.</p>
        <button type="button" id="btn-home-2" class="btn primary">Torna all'inizio</button>
      </section>
    </main>

    <script>
      import '../scripts/interview-client.ts';
    </script>

    <style>
      /* STRICT: the page never scrolls on the Y axis. */
      :global(html),
      :global(body) {
        height: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      :global(body) {
        color: var(--brand-text);
      }

      .app {
        height: 100dvh;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      /* Quint logotype on the start screen. */
      .brand-logo {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 180px;
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 auto 12px;
      }

      /* Only the active screen is shown; each fills the viewport. */
      .screen {
        display: none;
        height: 100dvh;
      }
      .app[data-screen='start'] #screen-start,
      .app[data-screen='code'] #screen-code,
      .app[data-screen='rules'] #screen-rules,
      .app[data-screen='interview'] #screen-interview,
      .app[data-screen='endq'] #screen-endq,
      .app[data-screen='paused'] #screen-paused,
      .app[data-screen='done'] #screen-done {
        display: flex;
      }

      /* Centered panels (start / code / endq / paused / done). */
      .panel {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .brand {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        color: var(--brand-purple);
      }
      .panel h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--brand-purple);
      }
      .hint {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .code-big {
        margin: 4px 0;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        color: var(--brand-purple);
        font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      }
      .error-line {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 1.2em;
        color: #d92d20;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .admin-link {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .admin-link:hover { color: var(--brand-orange); }

      /* Start-screen New / Resume paths. */
      .paths {
        display: flex;
        align-items: stretch;
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 4px;
      }
      .path {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 8px;
        min-width: 200px;
      }
      .path h2 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--brand-text);
      }
      .path-sep {
        align-self: center;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
      input[type='text'] {
        padding: 10px 12px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--brand-text);
        background: var(--brand-surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--brand-border);
        border-radius: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      input[type='text']:focus-visible {
        outline: 2px solid var(--brand-purple);
        outline-offset: 1px;
        border-color: var(--brand-purple);
      }
      #resume-code {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      }

      .btn {
        padding: 11px 22px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--brand-purple);
        background: var(--brand-surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--brand-border);
        border-radius: 999px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: border-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        border-color: var(--brand-orange);
        color: var(--brand-orange);
      }
      .btn.primary {
        color: #fff;
        background: var(--brand-purple);
        border-color: transparent;
      }
      .btn.primary:hover {
        color: #fff;
        background: var(--brand-orange);
      }
      .btn:disabled {
        opacity: 0.5;
        cursor: default;
      }
      .row {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      /* Interview screen: fixed top bar, stage fills, fixed bottom bar. */
      .interview {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .topbar {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 10px 18px calc(10px);
        padding-top: calc(10px + env(safe-area-inset-top, 0px));
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--brand-border);
      }
      .progress {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .completed {
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .timer {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
        color: var(--brand-purple);
      }
      .timer[data-warn='warn'] {
        color: var(--brand-orange);
      }
      .timer[data-warn='critical'] {
        color: #d92d20;
      }

      .stage {
        position: relative;
        flex: 1;
        min-height: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 16px;
      }
      #avatar-video {
        /* Size is driven by the box, NOT the stream's intrinsic resolution.
           Tavus ramps resolution up over the first seconds (adaptive bitrate); relying
           on intrinsic size makes the video start small and grow. A fixed 16:9 box with
           a max-width keeps both providers at a stable, identical, well-visible size. */
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 960px;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        max-height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: #000;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      }

      .meter {
        position: absolute;
        top: 22px;
        left: 22px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
        color: #e8eaed;
        background: rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.66);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 999px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        pointer-events: none;
      }
      .meter[hidden] {
        display: none;
      }
      .meter-icon {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .meter-cost {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #d9c9f0;
      }
      .meter-credits {
        color: #9aa0aa;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
      .meter-credits[hidden] {
        display: none;
      }
      .meter-credits[data-low='true'] {
        color: #fbbf24;
      }
      .meter-credits[data-low='critical'] {
        color: #f87171;
      }

      .caption {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 14px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        max-width: min(80%, 720px);
        max-height: calc(100% - 28px);
        margin: 0;
        padding: 6px 14px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        color: #cbd5e1;
        background: rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.6);
        border-radius: 10px;
        white-space: normal;
        overflow-wrap: break-word;
        overflow-y: auto;
        text-align: center;
        pointer-events: none;
      }
      .caption:empty {
        display: none;
      }

      /* Small mirrored self-view in the corner (the camera indicator is unsuppressable,
         so we keep the feed visible and expected). Hidden until a stream is attached. */
      .self-view {
        position: absolute;
        right: 22px;
        bottom: 22px;
        width: 132px;
        height: 99px;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: #000;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        transform: scaleX(-1);
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 2;
      }
      .self-view[hidden] {
        display: none;
      }

      .bar {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 12px 16px calc(16px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px));
      }
      .status {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
        min-height: 1.2em;
      }
      .status[data-state='listening'] {
        color: var(--brand-lavender);
      }
      .status[data-state='speaking'] {
        color: var(--brand-purple);
      }
      .status[data-state='ready'] {
        color: var(--brand-purple);
      }
      .status[data-state='connecting'] {
        color: var(--brand-orange);
      }
      .status[data-state='waiting'] {
        color: var(--brand-orange);
      }
      .status[data-state='error'] {
        color: #d92d20;
      }

      .pulsantone {
        --accent: var(--brand-purple);
        min-width: 240px;
        padding: 16px 40px;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #fff;
        background: var(--accent);
        border: none;
        border-radius: 999px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: transform 0.08s ease, filter 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(119, 26, 175, 0.35);
      }
      .pulsantone:hover {
        filter: brightness(1.06);
      }
      .pulsantone:active {
        transform: translateY(1px);
      }
      .pulsantone[data-on='true'] {
        --accent: #ef4444;
        color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.35);
      }
      .pulsantone:disabled {
        opacity: 0.6;
        cursor: default;
        box-shadow: none;
      }

      /* Segmented provider toggle + consent (shared with the start screen). */
      .provider-toggle {
        display: inline-flex;
        padding: 3px;
        background: var(--brand-surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--brand-border);
        border-radius: 999px;
      }
      .provider-toggle label {
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      .provider-toggle input {
        position: absolute;
        opacity: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
      }
      .provider-toggle span {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 6px 18px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
        border-radius: 999px;
        transition: background 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
      }
      .provider-toggle input:checked + span {
        color: #fff;
        background: var(--brand-purple);
      }
      .consent {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 8px;
        max-width: 520px;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        line-height: 1.35;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
        cursor: pointer;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .consent input {
        margin-top: 2px;
        accent-color: var(--brand-purple);
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .rules-list {
        text-align: left;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0 0 0 1.2em;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 8px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--brand-text);
        max-width: 420px;
      }
      .rules-note {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.76rem;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
        max-width: 420px;
      }

      /* ── Pre-join device check ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
      .device-check {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 420px;
      }
      .device-check[hidden] {
        display: none;
      }
      .device-check-preview {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 320px;
        aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
        border-radius: 14px;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #000;
        border: 1px solid var(--brand-border);
      }
      #device-preview {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        /* Mirror the preview so it reads like a mirror to the candidate. */
        transform: scaleX(-1);
      }
      .device-check-mic {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 320px;
      }
      .device-check-mic-label {
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
      }
      .mic-bar {
        width: 100%;
        height: 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--brand-border);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .mic-bar-fill {
        width: 0%;
        height: 100%;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--brand-lavender);
        transition: width 0.08s linear, background 0.15s ease;
      }
      .mic-bar-fill[data-ok='true'] {
        background: #22a06b; /* semantic green — mic level is adequate */
      }
      .device-check-status {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 6px;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 320px;
      }
      .status-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
      }
      .status-item::before {
        content: '○';
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--brand-text-muted);
      }
      .status-item[data-ok='true'] {
        color: var(--brand-text);
      }
      .status-item[data-ok='true']::before {
        content: '✓';
        color: #22a06b;
      }
      .device-check-denied {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #d92d20;
        max-width: 360px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .device-check-denied[hidden] {
        display: none;
      }
      .device-check-hint {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 1.1rem;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--brand-orange);
        text-align: center;
      }
      .device-check-hint:empty {
        min-height: 0;
      }

      .toast {
        position: fixed;
        top: 16px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        padding: 10px 18px;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #fff;
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.92);
        border-radius: 999px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        z-index: 200;
        pointer-events: none;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }
